items.title: Power Grid raises capex to Rs 23,000 crore citing soaring electricity demand
items.description: For FY26, the capex will be in the range of about Rs 28,000-30,000 crore, up from Rs 20,000 crore as previously planned. For FY27, the Capex will be Rs 35,000 crore, instead of Rs 20,000 crore.
